text: Andrew Neal (born 11 October 1999) is an English cricketer. He made his first- class debut on 26 March 2019, for Leeds/Bradford MCCU against Derbyshire, as part of the Marylebone Cricket Club University fixtures. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Hertfordshire cricketers Category:Leeds/Bradford MCCU cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:English cricketers of the 21st century
